## Proposed Changes

### Step 0 Pre-processing

#### [MODIFY] [srt_sentence_parser.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/srt_sentence_parser.py)

Thêm function mới `correct_srt_with_txt()`:
- Input: SRT file path + TXT file path + api_client + tier
- Parse SRT → list cues (id, start, end, text)
- Read TXT → raw text
- Build LLM prompt: compare & correct
- Parse LLM response → corrected cues
- Convert corrected cues → `List[SRTSegment]` (same format as `parse_srt_file()`)
- Return: corrected segments (để `parse_srt_to_sentences()` xử lý tiếp như cũ)

#### [MODIFY] [video_pipeline.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/1.Prompt_Image/1.Prompt_Image/core/video_pipeline.py) — Step 0

Sửa `_run_step0()`:
- Khi gặp file `.srt`: tìm file `.txt` cùng tên trong cùng folder
  - **Nếu tìm thấy TXT pair** → gọi `correct_srt_with_txt()` → dùng corrected segments
  - **Nếu KHÔNG có TXT** → fallback: parse SRT như cũ (hiện tại) + fallback merge cues bằng lowercase heuristic
- Khi gặp file `.txt`: parse như cũ (đã có punctuation + inline timecodes)

